snippet.title: FUNNIEST ANIMALS EVER! - You will LAUGH AT EVERY SINGLE VIDEO!
snippet.description:
Would you just look how all these kittens, cats, puppies, dogs, pig, ferret, parrot, duck, horse, lizard,... behave, play, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! Only the best funny animal and pet moments and highlights! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
